     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      請跟我念
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      眾:
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      &Amacr;ma
     </span>
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      bhante.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      是，大德。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">
      禮敬佛陀
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Namo tassa bhagavato arahato samm&amacr;sambuddhasa (3 times
     </span>
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      )
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      禮敬於世尊，應供、正等正覺者
     </span>
