     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      我皈依佛，
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      我皈依法，
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      我皈依僧；
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Dutiyampi Buddhaṁ saranaṁ gacch&amacr;mi.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Dutiyampi Dhammaṁ saranaṁ gacch&amacr;mi.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Dutiyampi Saṁghaṁ saranaṁ gacch&amacr;mi.
     </span>
    </p>
