     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      (Y): &Amacr;ma Bhante
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      眾：是，大德。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; vertical-align:baseline">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">
      受八戒
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <ol style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt" type="1">
     <li style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:10pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 26.99pt; padding-left:0.01pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt; vertical-align:baseline">
      <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
       P&amacr;ṇ&amacr;tip&amacr;t&amacr; veramaṇi-sikkh&amacr;padaṁ sam&amacr;diy&amacr;mi.
      </span>
     </li>
    </ol>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      我受持離殺生學處；
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <ol start="2" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt" type="1">
     <li style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:10pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 25.19pt; padding-left:1.81pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt; vertical-align:baseline">
      <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
       Adinn&amacr;d&amacr;n&amacr; veramaṇi-sikkh&amacr;padaṁ sam&amacr;diy&amacr;mi.
      </span>
     </li>
    </ol>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      我受持離不與取學處；
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <ol start="3" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt" type="1">
     <li style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:10pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 26.99pt; padding-left:0.01pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt; vertical-align:baseline">
      <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
       Abrahmacariya veramaṇi-sikkh&amacr;padaṁ sam&amacr;diy&amacr;mi.
      </span>
     </li>
    </ol>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      我受持離非梵行學處；
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <ol start="4" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt" type="1">
     <li style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:10pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 26.99pt; padding-left:0.01pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt; vertical-align:baseline">
      <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
       Mus&amacr;v&amacr;d&amacr; veramaṇi-sikkh&amacr;padaṁ sam&amacr;diy&amacr;mi.
      </span>
     </li>
    </ol>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      我受持離虛妄語學處；
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <ol start="5" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt" type="1">
     <li style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:10pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 26.99pt; padding-left:0.01pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt; vertical-align:baseline">
      <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
       Sur&amacr;-meraya-majja-pam&amacr;daṭṭh&amacr;n&amacr; veramaṇi-sikkh&amacr;padaṁ sam&amacr;diy&amacr;mi.
      </span>
     </li>
    </ol>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      我受持離放逸之因的諸酒類學處；
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <ol start="6" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt" type="1">
     <li style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:10pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 26.99pt; padding-left:0.01pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt; vertical-align:baseline">
      <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
       Vik&amacr;la-bhojan&amacr; veramaṇi-sikkh&amacr;padaṁ sam&amacr;diy&amacr;mi.
      </span>
     </li>
    </ol>
    <p style="margin:0pt; padding-left:27pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-27pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      我受持離非時食學處；
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <ol start="7" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt" type="1">
     <li style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:10pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 26.99pt; padding-left:0.01pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt; vertical-align:baseline">
      <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
       Nacca g&imacr;ta v&amacr;dita vis&umacr;kadassana, m&amacr;l&amacr;gandha vilepana dh&amacr;rana maṇḍana vibh&umacr;sanaṭṭh&amacr;n&amacr; veramaṇi-sikkh&amacr;padaṁ sam&amacr;diy&amacr;mi.
      </span>
     </li>
    </ol>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      我受持離觀聽跳舞、唱歌、音樂、表演；妝飾、裝扮之因的穿戴花鬘、芳香、塗香學處；
     </span>
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <ol start="8" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt" type="1">
     <li style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:10pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 26.99pt; padding-left:0.01pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt; vertical-align:baseline">
      <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
       Ucc&amacr;sayana-mah&amacr;sayan&amacr; veramaṇi-sikkh&amacr;padaṁ sam&amacr;diy&amacr;mi.
      </span>
     </li>
    </ol>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      我受持離高、大床座學處。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Idaṁ me s&imacr;laṁ magga-phala-n&amacr;ṇassa paccayo hotu.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:11pt">
      願我持戒（的功德）成為證道果緣
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      (S): Appam&amacr;dena samp&amacr;detha
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      （西亞多）：具正念地完成所修！
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      (Y): &Amacr;ma Bhante
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      （眾）：是，大德。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">
      求授五
     </span>
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">
      戒
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-18pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline">
      (Y)
     </span>
     <span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">
      &nbsp;&nbsp;
     </span>
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Ahaṁ bhante, tisaraṇena saha, panca-s&imacr;laṁ, dhammaṁ y&amacr;c&amacr;mi, anuggahaṁ katv&amacr; s&imacr;laṁ detha, me bhante.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      尊者大德我（向您）求授三皈與五戒， 請慈悲地滿足我的請求。
