     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Karaṇiya-matthakusalena
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Yaṁ ta santaṁ padaṁ abhisamecca,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Sakko uj&umacr; ca suhuj&umacr; ca,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Suvaco cassa mudu anatim&amacr;ni.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      一個精於行善，並為涅槃的終極安寧激勵的人應該修習(三種行）
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      他應當能幹，正直，極正直，順從，溫和，不傲慢。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
