     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Appagabbho kulesva-nanugiddho.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 34.2pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      應當知足，易養，少俗務，生活簡單（少擁有），收攝六根，處事謹慎不魯莽，不執著家庭（信眾）。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Na ca khudda-m&amacr;care kinci,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Yena vinn&umacr; pare upavadeyyuṁ,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Sukhino v&amacr; khemino hontu,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Sabbasatt&amacr; bhavantu sukkhitatt&amacr;.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      不應犯任何事後受智者指責的過錯，哪怕極其微小。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      願所有眾生喜樂，平安。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      願所有眾生心有喜樂。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Ye keci p&amacr;ṇabh&umacr;tatthi,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Tas&amacr; v&amacr; th&amacr;var&amacr; vanavases&amacr;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      D&imacr;gh&amacr; v&amacr; ye va mahant&amacr;,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Majjhim&amacr; rassak&amacr; aṇuka-th&umacr;l&amacr;.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Diṭṭh&amacr; v&amacr; ye va adiṭṭh&amacr;,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Ye va d&umacr;re vasanti avid&umacr;re,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Bh&umacr;t&amacr; va sambhaves&imacr;va,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Sabba-satt&amacr; bhavantu sukhitt&amacr;.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      一切眾生，不論柔弱或強壯，或長，大，或中等，短小，或小或肥大（圓滾），可見或不可見，遠或近，已出生的，或未出生的。願一切眾生毫無例外的都快樂。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Na paro paraṁ nikubbetha,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      N&amacr;timannetha katthaci na kanci,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      By&amacr;rosan&amacr; paṭighasanna,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      N&amacr;nna-mannassa dukkha-miccheyya.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      願人們不欺騙或鄙視任何地方的任何人。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      願人們不以侮辱和惡意傷害任何人。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      M&amacr;t&amacr; yath&amacr; niyaṁ putta-,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      M&amacr;yus&amacr; ekaputta-manurakkhe,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Evam pi sabbabh&umacr;tesu,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      M&amacr;nasaṁ bh&amacr;vaye aparim&amacr;ṇaṁ.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      如母親願捨命保護獨子一樣，更應對一切眾生培養無量之心。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Mettanca sabba-lokasmi,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      M&amacr;nasaṁ bh&amacr;vaye aparim&amacr;ṇaṁ,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Uddhaṁ adho ca tiriyanca,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Asamb&amacr;dhaṁ avera-masapattaṁ.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      讓這無邊無際的慈心充滿整個世界，至上方，下方和週遭；
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      讓其無限制，無嗔心，無敵意。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Tiṭṭhaṁ caraṁ nisinno va,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Say&amacr;no y&amacr;vat&amacr;ssa vitamiddho,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Etaṁ satiṁ adhiṭṭheyya,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Brahma-metaṁ vih&amacr;ra-midha m&amacr;hu.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      無論是站，行，坐，臥，凡清醒時，都應當開發於此慈心的正念。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      此即（遵照佛陀教導的）當下的梵行。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Diṭṭhin ca anupaggamma,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      S&imacr;lav&amacr; dassanena sampanno,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Kamesu vineyya gedhaṁ
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Na hi j&amacr;tu ggabbhaseyya puna reti.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 34.2pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      不持守錯見，具德前有（初果的）正見，滅除了對感官慾望的執著，他決定不會再投胎輪迴。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:center; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Excerpt from Mah&amacr; Satipatth&amacr;na Sutta
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:center; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">
      大念處經摘錄
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Ek&amacr;yno ayaṁ bhikkhave maggo
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      比丘們，這是唯一的道路！！
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      satt&amacr;naṁ visuddhiy&amacr;,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      為使眾生得清淨，
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Soka-paridev&amacr;naṁ samatikkam&amacr;ya,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      克服悲哀和憂歎
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Dukkha-domanass&amacr;naṁ atthaṅgamaya,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      為了滅除痛苦和不幸。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      N&amacr;yasa adhigam&amacr;ya,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      為踏上聖道。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Nibb&amacr;nassa sacchikiriy&amacr;ya,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      為體證涅槃。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Yad idaṁ catt&amacr;ro Satipaṭṭh&amacr;n&amacr;.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      這條道路就是四念住。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Katame catt&amacr;ro?
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      哪四個呢？
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Idha bhikkave bhikkhu,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      比丘們，在此（教授裡），
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      k&amacr;ye k&amacr;y&amacr;nupass&imacr; viharati,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      比丘持續地就身體觀察身體。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      &amacr;t&amacr;pi samp&amacr;j&amacr;no satim&amacr;,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      精勤，覺知，正念
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      vineya loke abhijjh&amacr;-domanassaṁ.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      斷除對此世界的貪和嗔。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      vedan&amacr;su vedan&amacr;nupass&imacr; viharati,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      比丘持續地就受觀察受。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
