      &amacr;t&amacr;pi samp&amacr;j&amacr;no satim&amacr;,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      精勤，覺知，正念
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
