    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      vineya loke abhijjh&amacr;-domanassaṁ.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      斷除對此世界的貪和嗔。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      citte citt&amacr;nupass&imacr; viharati,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      比丘持續地就心觀察心。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      &amacr;t&amacr;pi samp&amacr;j&amacr;no satim&amacr;,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      精勤，覺知，正念
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      vineya loke abhijjh&amacr;-domanassaṁ;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      斷除對此世界的貪和嗔。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Dhamesu dhamm&amacr;nupass&imacr; viharati
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      比丘持續地就法觀察法。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      &amacr;t&amacr;pi samp&amacr;j&amacr;no satim&amacr;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      精勤，覺知，正念
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      vineya loke abhijjh&amacr;-domanassaṁ;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      斷除對此世界的貪和嗔。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 3pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 3pt; text-align:center; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">
      緣起
     </span>
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      (Paṭiccasamupp&amacr;da)
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:132%; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt; text-align:center; text-indent:18pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline">
      (
     </span>
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; vertical-align:baseline">
      Titth&amacr;yatana-sutta, Aṅgutara Nik&amacr;ya
     </span>
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline">
      )
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:120%; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 36pt; padding-left:36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Avijj&amacr;-paccay&amacr; saṅkh&amacr;r&amacr;.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      緣無明而有行,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Saṅkh&amacr;ra-paccay&amacr; vinn&amacr;ṇaṃ.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      緣行而有識
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Vinn&amacr;ṇa-paccay&amacr; n&amacr;mar&umacr;paṃ.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      緣識而有名色
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 36pt; padding-left:36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      N&amacr;mar&umacr;pa-paccay&amacr; saḷ&amacr;yatanaṃ.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      緣名色而有六處
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Saḷ&amacr;yatana-paccay&amacr; phasso.
     </span>
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      緣六處而有觸
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Phassa-paccay&amacr; vedan&amacr;.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      緣觸而有受
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Vedan&amacr;-paccay&amacr;
     </span>
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      taṇh&amacr;.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      緣受而有愛
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Taṇh&amacr;-paccay&amacr; up&amacr;d&amacr;naṃ.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      緣愛而有取
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Up&amacr;d&amacr;na-paccay&amacr; bhavo.
     </span>
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline">
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      緣取而有有
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Bhava-paccay&amacr; j&amacr;ti.
     </span>
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline">
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      緣有而有生
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      J&amacr;ti-paccay&amacr; jar&amacr;maraṇaṃ.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      緣生而有老死
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Soka-parideva-dukkha-domanass'up&amacr;y&amacr;s&amacr; saṃbhavanti.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      愁,歎,苦,憂,惱生起
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Evam'etassa kevalassa dukkha-kkhandhassa samudayo hoti.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      如此升起全苦蘊之集.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Avijj&amacr;ya tveva asesa-vir&amacr;ga-nirodh&amacr;, saṅkh&amacr;ra-nirodho.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      無明滅則行滅
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     &nbsp;
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Saṅkh&amacr;ra-nirodh&amacr; vinn&amacr;ṇa-nirodho.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      行滅則識滅
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Vinn&amacr;ṇa-nirodh&amacr; n&amacr;mar&umacr;pa-nirodho.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      識滅則名色滅
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      N&amacr;mar&umacr;pa-nirodh&amacr; saḷ&amacr;yatana-nirodho.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      名色滅則六入處滅
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Saḷ&amacr;yatana-nirodh&amacr; phassa-nirodho.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      六入處滅則觸滅
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Phassa-nirodh&amacr; vedan&amacr;-nirodho.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      觸滅則受滅
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Vedan&amacr;-nirodh&amacr; taṇh&amacr;-nirodho.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      受滅則愛滅
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Taṇh&amacr;-nirodh&amacr; up&amacr;d&amacr;na-nirodho.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      愛滅則取滅
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Up&amacr;d&amacr;na-nirodh&amacr; bhava-nirodho.
     </span>
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline">
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      取滅則有滅
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Bhavanirodh&amacr; j&amacr;tinirodho.
     </span>
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline">
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      有滅則生滅
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      J&amacr;tinirodh&amacr; jar&amacr;maraṇaṃ,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      生滅則老病死、
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Soka-parideva-dukkha-domanass'up&amacr;y&amacr;s&amacr; nirujjhanti.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      愁,歎,苦,憂,惱滅
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">
      Evametassakevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      如是，全苦蘊則滅。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
