    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="background-color:#fffeff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Dukkh&amacr; j&amacr;ti punappunaṃ,
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="background-color:#fffeff; font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      一次次的再生是痛苦的
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:64.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-64.8pt">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Gahak&amacr;raka diṭṭhosi
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:64.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-64.8pt">
     <span style="background-color:#fffeff; font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      哦，見到你了，造屋者！
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="background-color:#fffeff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Puna-gehaṃ na k&amacr;hasi.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="background-color:#fffeff; font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      你將不再造屋了。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="background-color:#fffeff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Sabb&amacr; te ph&amacr;suk&amacr; bhagg&amacr;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="background-color:#fffeff; font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      你的椽都已經斷裂
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="background-color:#fffeff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Gahak&umacr;ṭaṃ visaṅkhataṃ
     </span>
     <span style="background-color:#fffeff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline">
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="background-color:#fffeff; font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      棟樑也已被毀壞
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="background-color:#fffeff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Visaṅkh&amacr;ra-gataṃ cittaṃ
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:64.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-64.8pt">
     <span style="background-color:#fffeff; font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      心到達了無為
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; padding-left:100.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-100.8pt">
     <span style="background-color:#fffeff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Taṇh&amacr;naṃ khayam-ajjhag&amacr;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 1.8pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36.9pt">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      證得一切貪愛的滅盡
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 1.8pt; text-align:justify">
