      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 1.8pt; text-align:center">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Lakkhaṇattayaṁ
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 1.8pt; text-align:center">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 1.8pt; text-align:center">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      三法印相
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 1.8pt; text-align:justify">
     &nbsp;
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      "Sabbe saṅkh&amacr;r&amacr; anicc&amacr;" ti, yad&amacr; pann&amacr;ya passati.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      當他以智慧見到所有緣起法是無常相的時候，
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Atha nibbindati dukkhe, esa maggo visuddhiy&amacr;.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      他對苦（身心現象的痛苦輪迴）產生厭離，這是導向清淨（解脫）的正道。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Sabbe saṅkh&amacr;r&amacr; dukkh&amacr;" ti, yad&amacr; pann&amacr;ya passati.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      當他見以智慧見到所有緣起法是苦的時候
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Atha nibbindati dukkhe, esa maggo visuddhiy&amacr;.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      他對苦（身心現象的痛苦輪迴）產生厭離，這是導向清淨（解脫）的正道。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      "Sabbe dhamm&amacr; anatt&amacr;" ti, yad&amacr; pann&amacr;ya passati.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      當他見以智慧見到所有法非我的時候
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Atha nibbindati dukkhe, esa maggo visuddhiy&amacr;.
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 38.7pt; text-align:justify">
     <span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      他對苦（身心現象的痛苦輪迴）產生厭離，這是導向清淨（解脫）的正道。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:center; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Anattalakkhaṇa Sutta
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:center; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:mingliu; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">
      無我相經
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:center; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:14pt; vertical-align:baseline">
      (
     </span>
     <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline">
      Saṁyutta Nik&amacr;ya XXII, 59)
     </span>
     <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; vertical-align:baseline">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:center; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      相應部 22 蘊相應 59 經
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:130%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Evaṁ me sutaṁ. Ekaṁ samayaṁ
     </span>
     <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      &nbsp;
     </span>
     <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">
      Bhagav&amacr; B&amacr;r&amacr;ṇasiyaṁ viharati Isipatane Migad&amacr;ye. Tatra kho bhagav&amacr; pancavaggiye bhikkh&umacr; &amacr;mantesi "bhikkhavo"it. "Badante"ti te bhikkhu bhagavato paccasosuṁ. Bagav&amacr; etadavoca:
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:120%; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      如是我聞，某日，世尊在波羅奈鹿野苑的仙人墜落處。
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:120%; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">
      在那裡，世尊召喚[那]群五比丘們：
     </span>
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:120%; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt">
     <span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Arial Unicode MS'; font-size:12pt">
      「比丘們！」
